column2: SELECT TOP # passive.fiberid as fiberID, passive.ra, passive.dec, passive.z as z_noqso, passive.zerr as z_noqso_err, passive.logmass as passive_logmass, starforming.logmass as starforming_logmass, pca.mstellar_median as pca_logmass  FROM stellarMassPassivePort AS passive JOIN stellarMassStarformingPort AS starforming ON passive.specobjid =  starforming.specobjid JOIN stellarMassPCAWiscM1# AS pca ON passive.specobjid = pca.specobjid  WHERE pca.warning=# and passive.logmass > #
